erred. We conclude that\nthe proposed scheme provides a useful tool for magneto-seismologically\nexploiting QPPs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Sep 2015 13:38:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-14"}
